Subject: [PATCH] sched: RT-balance on new task

rt-balance when creating new tasks.

Signed-off-by: Ingo Molnar <mingo@elte.hu>

---
 kernel/sched.c |    1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

Index: linux-2.6.24.7-rt21/kernel/sched.c
===================================================================
--- linux-2.6.24.7-rt21.orig/kernel/sched.c	2008-10-08 22:22:59.000000000 -0400
+++ linux-2.6.24.7-rt21/kernel/sched.c	2008-10-08 22:23:00.000000000 -0400
@@ -1707,6 +1707,7 @@ void fastcall wake_up_new_task(struct ta
 		inc_nr_running(p, rq);
 	}
 	check_preempt_curr(rq, p);
+	wakeup_balance_rt(rq, p);
 	task_rq_unlock(rq, &flags);
 }
 
